tical ingenuity. The best hope is for Europe to revive and defend its legacy of universal egalitarianism, which benefits all parties by preserving the promise of equal representation.  a29 4320aEuropean Union. 0aEquality before the lawzEuropean Union countries. 0aRepresentative government and representationzEuropean Union countries. 0aCivil rightszEuropean Union countries.1 aHorvat, Srećko,eauthor.2 aColumbia University.bPress. 0aInsurrections.  aJN 30 Z55 2015c1hUAHS-Bi0162035237484  aJN 30 Z55 2015wLCc1i0162035237484d2/28/2015e2/19/2015lON_SHELFmUAHSSn1p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/11/2015  aJN30 .Z55 2015wLCc1i1007400482d3/12/2015lON_SHELFmGR_MACEWANp$32.71rYsYtBOOKu3/3/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/nb2008026295bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/70925543